# Homepage Listing Card — Compact Premium

**STATUS: COMPACT PREMIUM SSOT | Product Owner Final Authorization 2026-07-18**

Prior v3/v4 pixel freezes are superseded for presentation density. Card **structure and behaviour** remain: image, favourite, price, inclusive price, title, condition, rating, views.

## Compact Premium dimensions

- Radius: **16px**
- Title: **15–16px / 600**
- Price: **18px / 700**
- Secondary / views: **12–13px**
- Content padding: **10px**
- Favourite: **≥28×28** touch

## Allowed

- Compact Premium density/type/spacing within PO guidelines
- Image loading, click, favourite, rating, views, a11y, perf
- Grid column changes only across breakpoints

## Prohibited

- Removing price, inclusive price, condition, or rating
- Parallel listing card components
- Giant empty content blocks
- Touching Login/Register

